dct_title_s: Iowa and Wisconsin : chiefly from the map of J.N. Nicollet
dct_description_sm: Differs from edition also copyrighted in 1844 in that it includes map of Michigan on verso.; Relief shown by hachures.; Shows counties, Indian trails, Indian villages, cities, towns, and notable geographic features for Wisconsin, Iowa, Minnesota, Nebraska and the Dakotas.; Map of Michigan on verso.; "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1844 by Sidney E. Morse and Samuel Breese in the Clerks Office of the Southern District of New York."
dct_publisher_sm: Sidney E. Morse and Samuel Breese (New York), 1944
